**Bartender** | Extra Elected | Variant
__Basics__
The Elected Bartender can talk in the tavern without having their identity revealed.
__Details__
The Elected Bartender has a secret channel where they can talk. Every message in that channel will be sent anonymously in the tavern chat.
The Elected Bartender may immediately resign from their position at any time.
Usually the Bartender is a townsfolk role, however this variant is an elected role and has no impact on the alignment of the Elected Bartender.
By default there is no Bartender election, however the Bartender may be elected during a day without another election - so usually during Day 0. 

__Simplified__
The Elected Bartender can talk in the tavern without having their identity revealed.
